:126554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"依家和理非感覺上放軟晒手腳<br />\n成日淨係籌錢登報 雖然制語輿論係好<br />\n但政府咁厚面皮根本冇用<br />\n究竟有冇實際野做到？"},{"pid":"40c2fb720a4ad1770330025d56ce03c9126c3340","tid":1312139,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件 我要去醫院驗傷</code>"},{"pid":"f66da922f051e1c9c4fe6bbf9d8a8a36fffcb5af","tid":1312139,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"好似有人講過而家唔係戰爭 告唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b00cb34316a3063d75ae132fc0b9894e092dba","tid":1312139,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3db7075ba042cfe2522ee8b040ecc27930dc3a79","tid":1312139,"uid":275556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"曾經美國有幾單示威都成功告入"},{"pid":"434419d45024b911e1e3f4166a482ddfd5395e06","tid":1312139,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"只有主權國家間的爭端才可以提交國際法院裁決。"},{"pid":"1011560c59638ce1c02c3e6895bfe6884369ce3f","tid":1312139,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"推推!"}]}